      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Rinkt bija tat Kantei\npretti preekſch neﬀamahin Kahrtim / ka to Galdu nest warretu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch darrija arridsan\ntahs neﬀamas Kahrtis no Sittim-Rohka / un pahrwilke tahs ar\nSeltu/ka to Galdu nest warreja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrija tohs Rihkus / kam us Galdu bija buht/\nwinnâ Btohdas/ un winna Karvotes/un Kannês/un Kausts/ ar\nko tee apfegti taptu/no ſchihſſta\nSelta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch darrija arridsan\nweenu Lukturi no tihra Selta / zeeta Darbâ darrija wiꞥſch to\nLukturi/ winna Kahtu / un winna Sarrus / winna Kaustus/\nwinnâ Pohgas/un winna Puḱkes isſteepahs is ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Seſchi Sarri isſteepahs\nis winna Sahneem/ trihs Luktura Sarri no winna weenas Puḱfes / un trihs Luktura Sarri no\nwinna ohtras Puḱfes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weenâ Sarri bija trihs\nKautfini / it ka Mandetu-Reeksti/ weena Pohga/un weena Puḱfe/un ohtrâ Sarri (attal) trihs\nKautfini it ka Mandetu-Reeksti/\nweena Pohga un weena Puḱfe;\nta bija tee ſeſchi Sarri / kas no\nta Luktura isſteepahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet paſcha Luktura bija\ntſchetri Kautfini / it ka Mandetu-Reeksti / ar fawahm Pohgahin/\nun ar fawahm Puḱfehm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tist bija weena Pohga\nappafsch diwi Sarreem/ no teem\nisſteepdunees/ ta bija tas ar teem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch darrija arridsan\ntahs neﬀamas Kahrtis no Sittim-Rohka / un pahrwilke tahs ar\nSeltu/ka to Galdu nest warreja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrija tohs Rihkus / kam us Galdu bija buht/\nwinnâ Btohdas/ un winna Karvotes/un Kannês/un Kausts/ ar\nko tee apfegti taptu/no ſchihſſta\nSelta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No weena Tale\nSelta darrija wiꞥſch to\nfus winna Rihkus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrija arridsan\nweenu Lukturi no tihra Selta / zeeta Darbâ darrija wiꞥſch to\nLukturi/ winna Kahtu / un winna Sarrus / winna Kaustus/\nwinnâ Pohgas/un winna Puḱkes isſteepahs is ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch pahrwilke tahs\nweena Selta / winna Jezus Seenas aptahrt\nna Raggus / un winna tam weenu selta Krohn\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch taiſija\nta Rinkus pee ta / appa\nna Krohna/winna diwe\nrôs / us winna abbeje\nneem preekſch tahm na\nKahrtim / ar ko to nef\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrija\nneﬀamas Kahrtis no Sittim-Rohka / un pahrwilke tahs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch darrija\nto ſwehtu Swaidifcha\nun Riwehpinaſchanaſ-Ç\nſchihſſtabin jaukas\nSahlehm/pehz Apteeke\n"
    }
  ],
